node.text: Here’s to a community borne from mountains. Because, while seasons change, the mountains always endure. From big city or small, snowy town – we’re all skiers. And, when we stand together, we’re as tall as the mountains. #WeAreTheMTNS. 💚🏔💚 With gratitude for this amazing community, @IkonPass doubled renewal discounts for 20/21, and extended all savings until May 27. Together, we will endure.
